i20050301-0800 (Daniela) 

Launching an existing launch configuration created with i20050218 will fail. The
CompatibilityActivator class cannot be found, causing this bundle to fail during
activation and lots of subsequent ClassNotFoundExceptions/NoClassDefFoundErrors.

Creating a new launch configuration or running the existing one with -clean works.

As a side note, I noticed a new launch configuration will not create its own
org.eclipse.osgi location (is it using the same from the target?).
